<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-2922] $TRIAL is used with Python tests but not tested accordingly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2922</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I did not install trial at first, not knowing that I&apos;m going to need it. The twisted test does not check whether $TRIAL actually has been found by configure, it simply tries to call an empty command then, leading to a funny error message about the first argument not being executable.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The workaround is to simply install trial.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
